    "author": "@Cooliemasteroz",
    "author_channel_id": "UCrGWvcU8w3y04Lg5KYPpOkA",
    "text": "Good idea, it was probably therapeutic for yourself as well, you need to do what’s good for you sometimes. Another good project for a kid is a cable car, I made one for a friends kid who was 4 at the time and he was really intrigued. I think it was also good because it was set up out side and it got him out of the house a bit more. I also explained how it is a solution to a problem by showing him a picture of one set up across a huge gorge that was too difficult to put a road across and was easier to build than a bridge just to get him thinking.",
    "likes": 0,
    "published_at": "2020-09-13T23:39:44Z",
    "reply_count": 2,
    "replies": [
